commit.message: Fix byte compiler warnings
Resolve issue 'Support BSD mixer #4'

Work around broken amixer on Raspbian

On the current Raspbian the syntax

amixer set PCM 3%+

does not do the right thing, but the syntax

amixer set PCM 80%

still works. So the workaround is to get the current volume, add the nudge
value, then set the volume to the new absolute percent value.
Fix issue volume-raise-10 is broken #3
